\id 1KI - Dawuro Full Bible Latin Version 
\h 1 Kaatatuwaa 
\toc1 Koyro Kaatatuwaa Mas'aafaa 
\toc2 1 Kaatatuwaa 
\toc3 1 Kat. 
\mt1 Koyro Kaatatuwaa Mas'aafaa 
\imt1 Geluwaa 
\ip Kaatatuwaa Mas'aafaa koyro shaakuu, Sammeela mas'aafatuwaa laa"atuwaan doometteedda, Israa'eeliyaa biittaa kaatetuwaa taarikiyaappe atteeddawaa kaalliide odee. Mas'aafaa heezzu waanna waanna kifiletuwaan shaakki s'eellanaw danddayeetto. 
\ili 1. Solomone bare aawuwaa Daawita sa'aan Israa'eelanne Yihudaa kaatiyaa gidiyaawaanne Aa aawuwaa Daawita hayk'uwaabaa odee. 
\ili 2. K'ay ha mas'aafay Solomone kawutetsaa ek'uwaanne I ootseedda kiitaa odiyaa taarikiiyaa. I ootseedda oosotuwaappe odanaw doonaa kumiyaawe Yerusaalamen gimbbetteedda Geeshsha Golliyaa. 
\ili 3. Israa'eelii huup'issanne gedissa kawutetsaa geetettiide laa"u kesiide shaaketteeddawaanne he shaaketteedda kawutetsatuwaa Kiristtoos yelettanaappe kase, udduppuntso s'eetu laytsay gakkanaw dumma dumma mooddeedda kaatetuwaa taarikiyaa odee. 
\ip Ha laa"u mas'aafatuwan asaa kaaletsiyaa kaatii lo"anne iitanne geetettiide pirddettiyaawe, S'oossaw I ammanettiyaawaa keenaana. Hewaadankka k'ay he biittay dic'c'iyaa dichchaynne demmiyaa injjii he kaaletsiyaa kaatii S'oossaw ammanetteedawaa keenaana. Hara baggana k'ay allaga s'oossatoo goynneeddawenne azazettenan is's'eeddawe kaaletsiyaawanttakka kaalliyaa asaakka bashshaw afeedda. Huup'issa bagga kawutetsaa kaatetuu ubbaykka paac'iyaan kunddeeddino. Shin Yihudaa kaatetuwaa taarikii iitatuuwaakka lo"otuwaakka odee. 
\ip Kaatetuu mas'aafan koyro kifiliyaan daro eretteeddawanttu, S'oossaa doonaa gidiide timbbitiyaa k'aalaa odeeddanne Asay eek'aw goynnenna malanne S'oossaw azazettenan is's'enna mala, minisiide erisseedda timbbitiyaa odiyaa mino asatuwaa. Unttunttuppekka eretaa dariyaawe Eelaasa. Eelaasi Ba'aala k'eesetuwaana naasetteedda taarikiikka he sa'aan odetteedda (Shemppuwaa 18 s'eella). 
\iot Shemppatuwaa Ubbatoo Imetteedda K'antsa K'ofatuwaa 
